><div>I am so damn happy with how far I've come. I came out to my friends and family last year and my mental health and outlook on life has improved so much.

Being visible for people who are still in the closet is important to me and that's why I celebrate Pride. I spent decades ignoring, repressing, and compensating for how I felt inside. While I wish I had the courage to pursue my happiness earlier in life, I didn't feel safe/comfortable or ready to explore it until I was in my late 30s and that's valid too.

Maybe this post will find someone who's struggling with their sexuality or gender. Imgur has always been such an inclusive community and I always see such amazing support. You are never too old. Never too bald or hairy. It doesn't matter if you believe you can pass. You're allowed to explore what gender means to you. You are valid and this world is better with you in it... And if you don't agree I'll fight you over it!

Happy Pride! ?️‍⚧️</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Woi54fy</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Darkholynova]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Work vent</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/CHmW9lh</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/J7wuFx9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/v137Mw3.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1x3Tgoj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/20SMDOd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xGP027N.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/mi6jAxh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ViWIfaw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/CHmW9lh</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lappyrat92]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>RIP Donald Sutherland</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/e26bsQb</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NiWxSN2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Loved him as Oddball in Kelly's Heroes. Died today aged 88 after a long illness.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/e26bsQb</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[PrincePiggo]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>There’s Jesus then there’s Republican Jesus</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/6fqLw0S</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fiT25zx.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/6fqLw0S</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[