tle><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Rw858te</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YpZHl3T.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I officially have a bisexual flag up in the apartment now. Funny how the little things give us so much comfort.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yOv5Lpw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VqSlh0J.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bqqYpAw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Feeling saucy tonight</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/X64Yt10.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I got enough drugs to get me through my training next week and then meet with my doctor. Let's hope I can actually focus and do this.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XedxPSw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/H1DfoFS.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OSUeoEL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>First I need to actually find a guy and get into a situation like this. Then I will have to start wearing a bra. I just don't need one so I never do and my nipples are always poking out.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vk8aIZk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jPEgGcd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YDp1Deu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This has been a slippery slope. My ex called today gushing about how bad he felt about all the bad things he has done, and I didn't cave and say the words "I forgive you". I just said... It's all in the past. So yeah, that was weird.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RHzrkcW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/o53mAm9.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Ilj2ytG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wdOvMGU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I love my short shorts. I definitely love to dress provocatively,  it's very liberating.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BQfwz8j.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/49YF2Vy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UOQhUlC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/b2jT9Sj.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WBpeOql.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1vpu60f.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/D6oB2Aq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZXZq357.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Rw858te</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Losingit3000]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Shop small whenever you can</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/RxV4v0w</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="http